" Movement
noremap <C-H> <C-W>5<
noremap <C-L> <C-W>5>
noremap <C-J> <C-W>3-
noremap <C-K> <C-W>3+
noremap <C-N> gT
noremap <C-M> gt

"Remapping of Actual Keys
"Note: Made a major change. Now, carriage return returns a newline
imap jj <Esc>
nnoremap <CR> o<Esc>
nnoremap 0 ^
nnoremap ^ 0
nnoremap <Space> za
nmap S ciw
nmap Y y$

command! W write
command! Q quit
command! WQ wq
command! Wq wq

